        <item>
          <actionDate>2017-07-27</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill amends the federal judicial code to specify that U.S. district courts have jurisdiction on the basis of diversity of citizenship if at least one adverse party does not share the same citizenship as another adverse party. </p>]]></text>
